name: Deep Sea Mermaid
description:
Mermaids are mythological creatures who has a body like a woman from the waist to the head, while the body from the waist down resembles a fish.
   Many stories associate mermaids with dangerous events such as floods, storms, shipwrecks, and sinking. But in another story they are kind and generous creatures, helping stray sailors, give grace or fall in love with humans.
